dc_description_s: This line shapefile represents road centerlines in Mono County, CA. Last updated: 3/16/19. Mono (Calif.). Geographic Information Services. (2020). Available at: https://purl.stanford.edu/nv342vs5023 This work is licensed under a Creative Commons Attribution 4.0 International License This layer is presented in the WGS84 coordinate system for web display purposes.
